ed correctly.\\n  - `test_cli_interface.py`: Tests user interactions through the CLI, validating command processing and task management operations.\\n\\n### Next Steps\\n- Run the unit tests to ensure that all functionalities are working as expected.\\n- Gather feedback and make necessary adjustments based on testing results.\\n- Prepare for a potential deployment of the application to users.\\n\\nThe project is now fully set up and ready for the next phases of testing and refinement.\\n\\nARCHITECTURE COMPLETE\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"}}", "sender": "Architect_6fda33fc-6e9c-4a0c-9333-95968c0ba114/6fda33fc-6e9c-4a0c-9333-95968c0ba114", "receiver": "output_topic_6fda33fc-6e9c-4a0c-9333-95968c0ba114/6fda33fc-6e9c-4a0c-9333-95968c0ba114", "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.SEND", "type": "Message"}
