ks, and maintaining task data in a JSON format.\\\\n\\\\n## Features\\\\n- **Add Task**: Create a new task with a description.\\\\n- **View Tasks**: List all current tasks with their statuses (completed or not).\\\\n- **Mark Task as Done**: Update a task's status to completed.\\\\n- **Delete Task**: Remove a task from the list.\\\\n- **Persistent Storage**: Save tasks to a JSON file and load them at the start of the application.\\\\n\\\\n## Architecture\\\\nThe application is divided into the following modules:\\\\n1. **Task Management Module**: Handles task operations.\\\\n2. **JSON Handling Module**: Manages data serialization/deserialization in JSON.\\\\n3. **CLI Interface Module**: Processes user input/output.\\\\n\\\\nOverall, the CLI Todo application aims to provide a simple yet effective way to keep track of personal tasks.\\\"}\",\"name\":\"docs_write_file\"}],\"results\":[{\"content\":\"Successfully wrote to data/knowledge_base/cli_todo_app_testing.md\",\"name\":\"docs_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_NwZX5NNb211RYnb3pWsNvMNz\",\"is_error\":false},{\"content\":\"Successfully wrote to data/knowledge_base/cli_todo_app_overview.md\",\"name\":\"docs_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_5MRHZDPDjNO9EVpjFDtOl85n\",\"is_error\":false}]},\"inner_messages\":[{\"id\":\"def7b6e4-b240-4147-ab38-bfb3dd33f570\",\"source\":\"Architect\",\"models_usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":7229,\"completion_tokens\":486},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-03-17T07:13:08.998329Z\",\"content\":[{\"id\":\"call_NwZX5NNb211RYnb3pWsNvMNz\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"data/knowledge_base/cli_todo_app_testing.md\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"# CLI Todo App Testing Documentation\\\\n\\\\n## Overview\\\\nThis document provides insights into the testing strategy of the CLI Todo application, detailing the purpose and structure of the tests implemented.\\\\n\\\\n## Testing Structure\\\\nThe tests are organized into separate modules, each targeting specific functionalities within the CLI Todo applicatio